packaging for the following platforms:

redhat          - Redhat, Centos, OpenSUSE/SLES
debian          - Debian, Ubuntu
archlinux       - ArchLinux
slackware       - Slackware packaging
freebsd         - FreeBSD standalone package (not ports, not pkgng)
netbsd          - NetBSD standalon package (not ports, not pkgsrc)
windows         - WIX MSI installer setup creation
obs             - OpenSUSE build service (build.opensuse.org)
patches         - patches for all kind of sofwaere and systems,
                  needed when building Wolfame
